                            <comment id="12879017" author="eli" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2010 17:16:58 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Full test log attached.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12879830" author="eli" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2010 17:18:36 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Could this be due to the switch to Hadoop&apos;s local mode?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12879833" author="zjffdu" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2010 17:30:37 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I believe so, hadoop&apos;s local mode need much more memory. One solution fo this problem is to increase the heap space for test case by setting the Xmx argument&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12879846" author="daijy" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2010 17:58:06 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I also see this error couple of times. Sounds like we should increase the heap space.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12879874" author="rding" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2010 19:16:23 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 for commit. This should fix this OOM problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12879940" author="eli" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2010 22:30:27 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I confirmed this patch fixed the test failures. Thanks Daniel.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
